{
  "stem": "15393.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I mean it was all very dangerous what we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was absolutely stupid, almost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was so desperate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these people would, whoever, pick-- pick something like this up and find my mother and deliver.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she would bring, and that person would then leave a message somewhere, where I would see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you-- you know, somewhere where I would see a message would be left under the house, under a s stone, under some-- or make a-- make a sign, all is well, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That would be it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, Frau Wieth comes home and says, look, you won't be alone anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've got somebody for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I go, oh, my God, what has she done now?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because, in those days, you know, I really was smarter than she was, because she was not-- what should I say?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the same-- on the same planet as I was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, what have you done?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Who-- what do you mean, you've got somebody for me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where from?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Who is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she says, you know this chemist, what I get my medications from, you know, Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Podoshin. ?] You know, I-- I went to him, and I asked him if he doesn't know of anybody that I could possibly take into hiding, because I have you here.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he thought it was some kind of a trap, that she wants to trap him into something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He couldn't believe anybody in their-- in their right senses, you know, a German person, coming and saying a thing like this and asking-- asking, have you got somebody I'll take into hiding?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I haven't got anyone, of course not.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
